PEOPLE, Respondent, v. BIDDISON, Appellant. (Supreme Court, Appellate Division, First Department. October 15, 1909.) Proceeding by the People against Samuel N. Biddison.

With this case has been consolidated in this court cases bearing titles as follows: People v. Morris Berkowitz; Same v. Joseph Fuchs and Edward H. Strauss; Same v. John Green; Same v. Anthony Mareno; Same v. William Springer; Same v. Edgar A. Whitney.

No opinions. Motions to dismiss appeals granted, unless the appellants have their appeals ready for argument at the December term. Orders filed.
